        "content": "<p>It indeed sounds like a bug in wasmtime.</p>",
        "id": 291565678,
        "sender_full_name": "Dan Gohman",
        "timestamp": 1659355990
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It looks like your test isn't setting <code>OFLAGS_CREAT</code>.</p>",
        "id": 291566454,
        "sender_full_name": "Lann Martin",
        "timestamp": 1659356435
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I don't know about WASI, but POSIX requires both flags for that behavior.</p>",
        "id": 291566594,
        "sender_full_name": "Lann Martin",
        "timestamp": 1659356515
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Indeed that appears to be what <code>cap-std-sync</code> expects:  <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/fa36e86f2c45f427e9d8a16f559a2515213ab3d4/crates/wasi-common/cap-std-sync/src/dir.rs#L32-L34\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/fa36e86f2c45f427e9d8a16f559a2515213ab3d4/crates/wasi-common/cap-std-sync/src/dir.rs#L32-L34</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/fa36e86f2c45f427e9d8a16f559a2515213ab3d4/crates/wasi-common/cap-std-sync/src/dir.rs#L32-L34\" style=\"background-image: url(https\\:\\/\\/uploads\\.zulipusercontent\\.net\\/0e5f87abe99154b514e75e8c93aa40614538870d\\/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f633732336235303437396236333636323964646666346438656464646337323338363266643161633036313239306463323132343238386438323431333735352f62797465636f6465616c6c69616e63652f7761736d74696d65)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/fa36e86f2c45f427e9d8a16f559a2515213ab3d4/crates/wasi-common/cap-std-sync/src/dir.rs#L32-L34\" title=\"wasmtime/dir.rs at fa36e86f2c45f427e9d8a16f559a2515213ab3d4 路 bytecodealliance/wasmtime\">wasmtime/dir.rs at fa36e86f2c45f427e9d8a16f559a2515213ab3d4 路 bytecodealliance/wasmtime</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">A standalone runtime for WebAssembly. Contribute to bytecodealliance/wasmtime development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div>",
